ibus-libpinyin

Intelligent Pinyin engine based on libpinyin for IBus

Description
It includes a Chinese Pinyin input method and a Chinese ZhuYin (Bopomofo) input method based on libpinyin for IBus.

Install:

Step 1. Get dependencies ibus-1.0-dev, sqlite3, libsqlite3-dev, libdb-dev and libdb++-dev

Step 2. Get latest libpinyin tarball

(follow these instructions)

https://github.com/libpinyin/ibus-libpinyin/wiki/Installation

Note that you should use ./configure then make && make install instead of using "./autogen.sh" like in the instructions

Step 3. Run ./autogen.sh on this repo 
